# Secrets and Sensitive Info

- NEVER echo tokens, passwords, or credentials in chat.
- NEVER generate sample tokens. Use `<not in chat>` instead.
- Assume `.env`, `appsettings.*.json`, and config files may contain secrets.
- Always redact before displaying or committing.
